        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "khorbah",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", which, as Dr. Payne Smith remarks, is \"used only of places which, having once been inhabited, have then fallen into ruin.\" Hebrew is rich in synonyms for the idea of \"desolation.\" ",
        "children": []
